# 📊 Business Intelligence Sales Dashboard

End-to-end Business Intelligence and Sales Analytics project developed with Python, Pandas, SQLite, SQL and Power BI.

This project simulates a real-world BI workflow, including:

- Data extraction and preprocessing
- Feature engineering
- SQL analytics
- KPI generation
- Revenue analysis
- Customer analytics
- Product analytics
- Geographic analytics
- Automated chart generation
- Power BI dashboard integration

---

# 🚀 Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- SQLite
- SQL
- Matplotlib
- Power BI
- CSV
- Data Analysis
- Business Intelligence

---

# 📂 Project Structure

```bash
Business-Intelligence-Sales-Dashboard/
│
├── dados/
│   ├── superstore_sales.csv
│   └── sales_clean.csv
│
├── dashboard/
│
├── graficos/
│   ├── monthly_growth.png
│   ├── revenue_by_category.png
│   ├── revenue_by_month.png
│   ├── revenue_by_state.png
│   ├── top_customers.png
│   └── top_products.png
│
├── queries/
│   ├── total_revenue.sql
│   ├── revenue_by_month.sql
│   ├── revenue_by_category.sql
│   ├── top_products.sql
│   └── top_customers.sql
│
├── sales_analysis.py
├── sales_analytics.db
├── README.md
└── LICENSE
```

---

# 📊 Features

## ✔ Data Cleaning and Preprocessing

- Datetime conversion
- Null validation
- Data normalization
- Dataset preparation

---

## ✔ Feature Engineering

Creates analytical features such as:

- Year
- Month
- Month Name
- Revenue KPIs
- Temporal metrics

---

## ✔ SQL Analytics

Uses modular SQL queries for:

- Revenue analysis
- Product analysis
- Customer analysis
- KPI generation
- Business metrics

---

## ✔ Revenue Analytics

Performs exploratory business analysis including:

- Revenue by month
- Revenue growth
- Revenue by category
- Revenue by state
- Top products
- Top customers

---

## ✔ Data Visualization

Automatically generates analytical charts using Matplotlib.

---

## ✔ Power BI Integration

The cleaned dataset can be directly connected to Power BI dashboards for:

- Interactive filters
- Executive dashboards
- Dynamic analytics
- Business monitoring

---

# 📈 Main Insights

## 📅 Revenue Growth Patterns

Monthly growth analysis identifies seasonal fluctuations and business expansion periods.

---

## 🌎 Geographic Revenue Distribution

Some states concentrate significantly higher revenue generation.

---

## 📦 Product Concentration

A small group of products represents a major portion of total sales.

---

## 👥 Customer Revenue Concentration

Top customers contribute disproportionately to total business revenue.

